<br>
If I got a tell as my cleric telling me to find my way to the frenzy room to rez someone because they were stupid enough to bind there, their enchanter went oom, their monk FD, their wizard over aggroed, and their cleric isn't 49 yet or probably dead too, I would have absolutely no sympathy for the poor schmuck.  I'm a compassionate person especially while playing my cleric, hey I've had my fair share of deaths and bad luck, but stupidity is not an excuse. ;)<br>
<br>
I'm not saying you're stupid to bind there, if it works for you, great, you have great luck.  I just personally would never bind in a dungeon unless I was with a group I trusted such as a guild.  Hence why I bound my wizard in the Efreeti room in Sol B during a guild raid to port people out prior to translocates. :) <p><CENTER>
